    {'name':'runOneSpin','purpose':'Execute one paid base-game round and, when selected, one triggered feature session.','inputs':[{'name':'bet_fixed_coins','type':'int','shape':'[1]','required_value':planner['game']['base_bet_fixed_coins']},{'name':'feature_choice','type':'enum FeatureChoice','shape':'[1]','allowed':['NONE','FREE_SPINS','BLITZ_SPINS'],'condition':'Required only when 3+ base SCAT triggers feature selection.'},{'name':'rng','type':'RNG source','shape':'stateful'}],'outputs':[{'name':'SpinResult','type':'struct','shape':'[1]'}],'global_dependencies':['NO_OF_REELS','NO_OF_ROWS','probTable.ReelsetWeights','BG1_Reels','BG1_ReelSize','BG2_Reels','BG2_ReelSize'],'pseudocode':['Select BG1 or BG2 using ReelsetWeights.','Generate base PayWindow.','Resolve additional COR injection.','Evaluate ways and SCAT wins.','Resolve Collect wins.','If base SCAT count is less than 3, return base result.','If feature choice is FREE_SPINS, award free spins by base SCAT count and call FreeGameFeature_1.','If feature choice is BLITZ_SPINS, award blitz spins by base SCAT count and call FreeGameFeature_2.','Return total win and event trace.']},
